      "text": "~ In this case placement is depend on many factors\n\n    - communation skill\n    - CGPA\n    - Apptitude skills\n    - problem solving skill\n    - how to handle the things\n    -projects\n    -behavioural skill\n    - interview performance\npatterns are going to be difficult   ->>>> AI is needed\n",
