      "text": "~ step 4:-   Identifying Stakeholder :-\n\n    stakeholder mapping :-\n\n    - University Management :- increase placements ratio\n    - Students :- prepare for interview\n    - parents :- student success\n    - placement officer :- help more students get placed\n    - faculty :- improve student outcome\n    - placement cell :- organize preparation activites",
