      "seed": 1781979069,
      "version": 458,
      "versionNonce": 1025688083,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1781572182650,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Step 5 :- Define the AI task :-\n\n    ~ placement prediction :-\n        - classification problem\n            - output -> placed = yes / placed = no\n                - binary classification problem\n\n    ~ Ranking problem :-\n        - top student getting placed first\n\n    ~ identify weak area of each student :-\n        - students work on and perform better in interview\n\n    ~ suggest companies match with student profile\n        - student give interview in that companies and getting placed\n ",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Step 5 :- Define the AI task :-\n\n    ~ placement prediction :-\n        - classification problem\n            - output -> placed = yes / placed = no\n                - binary classification problem\n\n    ~ Ranking problem :-\n        - top student getting placed first\n\n    ~ identify weak area of each student :-\n        - students work on and perform better in interview\n\n    ~ suggest companies match with student profile\n        - student give interview in that companies and getting placed\n ",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
