      "updated": 1781572849382,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Step 6 :-   defining the success metrices :-\n\n    - Technical metrics :-\n        - accuracy\n        - precision\n        - recall\n        - F1 score\n        - ROC-AUC\n\n    - Business metrices :-\n            - placement ratio improve\n            - more student get placed\n            - aptitude score improve\n            - mock interview score improve ",
