      "updated": 1781574021402,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "~ step 7 :-    Defining constraints :-\n\n                every AI project operates under constraints\n\n~ constraints type :- \n\n    - time constraints :-\n        - before end of the 3nd year\n\n     - data constraints:-\n           - certain information may not exist:-\n                - mental health indicator\n                - family circumstances\n                - updated financial records\n\n       - ethical constraints\n            - student should not be harmed\n                    - is the model biased against particular group\n                    - can student appeal dicisions?\n                     - student  data is not share to any other  \n                        company without permission",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "~ step 7 :-    Defining constraints :-\n\n                every AI project operates under constraints\n\n~ constraints type :- \n\n    - time constraints :-\n        - before end of the 3nd year\n\n     - data constraints:-\n           - certain information may not exist:-\n                - mental health indicator\n                - family circumstances\n                - updated financial records\n\n       - ethical constraints\n            - student should not be harmed\n                    - is the model biased against particular group\n                    - can student appeal dicisions?\n                     - student  data is not share to any other  \n                        company without permission",
